===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|رَبِيعُ الآخِرُ}}''' {{IPAchar|(rabí:ʕu l-’āχir)}} {{m}}

#[[Rabia II]], the fourth of the twelve months of the Muslim lunar calendar, each beginning with a [[new moon]]. [[Rabia II]] means "last of spring" in Arabic.

